---
title: Oven-Ready BBQ Pork Chops with Biscuits & Lemony Green Beans (trays included)
description: Pork chops are always a dinner winner. They’re satisfying, speedy, and so versatile, which is why our chefs are always thinking up new ways to take them to the next level. This week’s version comes together in just 30 minutes, with minimal cleanup required thanks to our handy oven-ready aluminum trays. We glaze spice-rubbed pork chops with tangy-sweet BBQ sauce, then roast right alongside ready-to-bake biscuits and lemony green beans. We call that the perfect busy weeknight meal.
